events.name: Oklahoma City Thunder at Denver Nuggets

headlines.description: — Nikola Jokic had 27 points and 12 rebounds before calling it an early night as the Denver Nuggets routed the Oklahoma City Thunder 119-101 on Tuesday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Jokic scores 27 in 3 quarters, Nuggets rout Thunder 119-101

events.name: New Orleans Pelicans at Utah Jazz

headlines.description: — Donovan Mitchell had 28 points and seven rebounds, and the Utah Jazz beat the New Orleans Pelicans 118-102 on Tuesday night for their sixth straight victory.
